verses.text_plain: The sons of Levi; Gershon, Kohath, and Merari.
verses.verse_html:
1The sons of Levi; Gershon, Kohath, and Merari. ▼
▼ Gershon: or, Gershom

verses.text_plain: And the sons of Kohath; Amram, Izhar, and Hebron, and Uzziel.
verses.verse_html: 2And the sons of Kohath; Amram, Izhar, and Hebron, and Uzziel.

verses.text_plain: And the children of Amram; Aaron, and Moses, and Miriam. The sons also of Aaron; Nadab, and Abihu, Eleazar, and Ithamar.
verses.verse_html: 3And the children of Amram; Aaron, and Moses, and Miriam. The sons also of Aaron; Nadab, and Abihu, Eleazar, and Ithamar.

verses.text_plain: Eleazar begat Phinehas, Phinehas begat Abishua,
verses.verse_html: 4Eleazar begat Phinehas, Phinehas begat Abishua,

verses.text_plain: And Abishua begat Bukki, and Bukki begat Uzzi,
verses.verse_html: 5And Abishua begat Bukki, and Bukki begat Uzzi,

verses.text_plain: And Uzzi begat Zerahiah, and Zerahiah begat Meraioth,
verses.verse_html: 6And Uzzi begat Zerahiah, and Zerahiah begat Meraioth,

verses.text_plain: Meraioth begat Amariah, and Amariah begat Ahitub,
verses.verse_html: 7Meraioth begat Amariah, and Amariah begat Ahitub,

verses.text_plain: And Ahitub begat Zadok, and Zadok begat Ahimaaz,
verses.verse_html: 8And Ahitub begat Zadok, and Zadok begat Ahimaaz,

verses.text_plain: And Ahimaaz begat Azariah, and Azariah begat Johanan,
verses.verse_html: 9And Ahimaaz begat Azariah, and Azariah begat Johanan,

verses.text_plain: And Johanan begat Azariah, (he it is that executed the priest’s office in the temple that Solomon built in Jerusalem:)
verses.verse_html:
10And Johanan begat Azariah, (he it is that executed the priest’s office in the temple that Solomon built in Jerusalem:) ▼
▼ in the temple: Heb. in the house

footnotes.body_text: ▼ in the temple: Heb. in the house
footnotes.body_html: ▼ in the temple: Heb. in the house

verses.text_plain: And Azariah begat Amariah, and Amariah begat Ahitub,
verses.verse_html: 11And Azariah begat Amariah, and Amariah begat Ahitub,

verses.text_plain: And Ahitub begat Zadok, and Zadok begat Shallum,
verses.verse_html:
12And Ahitub begat Zadok, and Zadok begat Shallum, ▼
▼ Shallum: or, Meshullam

verses.text_plain: And Shallum begat Hilkiah, and Hilkiah begat Azariah,
verses.verse_html: 13And Shallum begat Hilkiah, and Hilkiah begat Azariah,

verses.text_plain: And Azariah begat Seraiah, and Seraiah begat Jehozadak,
verses.verse_html: 14And Azariah begat Seraiah, and Seraiah begat Jehozadak,

verses.text_plain: And Jehozadak went into captivity, when the Lord carried away Judah and Jerusalem by the hand of Nebuchadnezzar.
verses.verse_html: 15And Jehozadak went into captivity, when the Lord carried away Judah and Jerusalem by the hand of Nebuchadnezzar.

verses.text_plain: The sons of Levi; Gershom, Kohath, and Merari.
verses.verse_html:
16The sons of Levi; Gershom, Kohath, and Merari. ▼
▼ Gershom: or, Gershon

verses.text_plain: And these be the names of the sons of Gershom; Libni, and Shimei.
verses.verse_html: 17And these be the names of the sons of Gershom; Libni, and Shimei.

verses.text_plain: And the sons of Kohath were, Amram, and Izhar, and Hebron, and Uzziel.
verses.verse_html: 18And the sons of Kohath were, Amram, and Izhar, and Hebron, and Uzziel.

verses.text_plain: The sons of Merari; Mahli, and Mushi. And these are the families of the Levites according to their fathers.
verses.verse_html: 19The sons of Merari; Mahli, and Mushi. And these are the families of the Levites according to their fathers.

verses.text_plain: Of Gershom; Libni his son, Jahath his son, Zimmah his son,
verses.verse_html: 20Of Gershom; Libni his son, Jahath his son, Zimmah his son,

verses.text_plain: Joah his son, Iddo his son, Zerah his son, Jeaterai his son.
verses.verse_html:
21Joah his son, Iddo his son, Zerah his son, Jeaterai his son. ▼
▼ Joah: or, Ethan
 , ▼
▼ Iddo: or, Adaiah
 , ▼
▼ Jeaterai: also called, Ethni

footnotes.body_html: ▼ Jeaterai: also called, Ethni

verses.text_plain: The sons of Kohath; Amminadab his son, Korah his son, Assir his son,
verses.verse_html:
22The sons of Kohath; Amminadab his son, Korah his son, Assir his son, ▼
▼ Amminadab: or, Izhar

verses.text_plain: Elkanah his son, and Ebiasaph his son, and Assir his son,
verses.verse_html: 23Elkanah his son, and Ebiasaph his son, and Assir his son,

verses.text_plain: Tahath his son, Uriel his son, Uzziah his son, and Shaul his son.
verses.verse_html: 24Tahath his son, Uriel his son, Uzziah his son, and Shaul his son.

verses.text_plain: And the sons of Elkanah; Amasai, and Ahimoth.
verses.verse_html: 25And the sons of Elkanah; Amasai, and Ahimoth.

verses.text_plain: As for Elkanah: the sons of Elkanah; Zophai his son, and Nahath his son,
verses.verse_html:
26As for Elkanah: the sons of Elkanah; Zophai his son, and Nahath his son, ▼
▼ Zophai: or, Zuph

verses.text_plain: Eliab his son, Jeroham his son, Elkanah his son.
verses.verse_html: 27Eliab his son, Jeroham his son, Elkanah his son.

verses.text_plain: And the sons of Samuel; the firstborn Vashni, and Abiah.
verses.verse_html:
28And the sons of Samuel; the firstborn Vashni, and Abiah. ▼
▼ Vashni: called also Joel

footnotes.body_html: ▼ Vashni: called also Joel

verses.text_plain: The sons of Merari; Mahli, Libni his son, Shimei his son, Uzza his son,
verses.verse_html: 29The sons of Merari; Mahli, Libni his son, Shimei his son, Uzza his son,

verses.text_plain: Shimea his son, Haggiah his son, Asaiah his son.
verses.verse_html: 30Shimea his son, Haggiah his son, Asaiah his son.

verses.text_plain: And these are they whom David set over the service of song in the house of the Lord, after that the ark had rest.
verses.verse_html: 31And these are they whom David set over the service of song in the house of the Lord, after that the ark had rest.

verses.text_plain: And they ministered before the dwelling place of the tabernacle of the congregation with singing, until Solomon had built the house of the Lord in Jerusalem: and then they waited on their office according to their order.
verses.verse_html: 32And they ministered before the dwelling place of the tabernacle of the congregation with singing, until Solomon had built the house of the Lord in Jerusalem: and then they waited on their office according to their order.

verses.text_plain: And these are they that waited with their children. Of the sons of the Kohathites: Heman a singer, the son of Joel, the son of Shemuel,
verses.verse_html:
33And these are they that waited with their children. Of the sons of the Kohathites: Heman a singer, the son of Joel, the son of Shemuel, ▼
▼ waited: Heb. stood

verses.text_plain: The son of Elkanah, the son of Jeroham, the son of Eliel, the son of Toah,
verses.verse_html: 34The son of Elkanah, the son of Jeroham, the son of Eliel, the son of Toah,

verses.text_plain: The son of Zuph, the son of Elkanah, the son of Mahath, the son of Amasai,
verses.verse_html: 35The son of Zuph, the son of Elkanah, the son of Mahath, the son of Amasai,

verses.text_plain: The son of Elkanah, the son of Joel, the son of Azariah, the son of Zephaniah,
verses.verse_html: 36The son of Elkanah, the son of Joel, the son of Azariah, the son of Zephaniah,

verses.text_plain: The son of Tahath, the son of Assir, the son of Ebiasaph, the son of Korah,
verses.verse_html: 37The son of Tahath, the son of Assir, the son of Ebiasaph, the son of Korah,

verses.text_plain: The son of Izhar, the son of Kohath, the son of Levi, the son of Israel.
verses.verse_html: 38The son of Izhar, the son of Kohath, the son of Levi, the son of Israel.

verses.text_plain: And his brother Asaph, who stood on his right hand, even Asaph the son of Berachiah, the son of Shimea,
verses.verse_html: 39And his brother Asaph, who stood on his right hand, even Asaph the son of Berachiah, the son of Shimea,

verses.text_plain: The son of Michael, the son of Baaseiah, the son of Malchiah,
verses.verse_html: 40The son of Michael, the son of Baaseiah, the son of Malchiah,

verses.text_plain: The son of Ethni, the son of Zerah, the son of Adaiah,
verses.verse_html: 41The son of Ethni, the son of Zerah, the son of Adaiah,

verses.text_plain: The son of Ethan, the son of Zimmah, the son of Shimei,
verses.verse_html: 42The son of Ethan, the son of Zimmah, the son of Shimei,

verses.text_plain: The son of Jahath, the son of Gershom, the son of Levi.
verses.verse_html: 43The son of Jahath, the son of Gershom, the son of Levi.

verses.text_plain: And their brethren the sons of Merari stood on the left hand: Ethan the son of Kishi, the son of Abdi, the son of Malluch,
verses.verse_html:
44And their brethren the sons of Merari stood on the left hand: Ethan the son of Kishi, the son of Abdi, the son of Malluch, ▼
▼ Kishi: or, Kushaiah

verses.text_plain: The son of Hashabiah, the son of Amaziah, the son of Hilkiah,
verses.verse_html: 45The son of Hashabiah, the son of Amaziah, the son of Hilkiah,

verses.text_plain: The son of Amzi, the son of Bani, the son of Shamer,
verses.verse_html: 46The son of Amzi, the son of Bani, the son of Shamer,

verses.text_plain: The son of Mahli, the son of Mushi, the son of Merari, the son of Levi.
verses.verse_html: 47The son of Mahli, the son of Mushi, the son of Merari, the son of Levi.

verses.text_plain: Their brethren also the Levites were appointed unto all manner of service of the tabernacle of the house of God.
verses.verse_html: 48Their brethren also the Levites were appointed unto all manner of service of the tabernacle of the house of God.

verses.text_plain: But Aaron and his sons offered upon the altar of the burnt offering, and on the altar of incense, and were appointed for all the work of the place most holy, and to make an atonement for Israel, according to all that Moses the servant of God had commanded.
verses.verse_html: 49But Aaron and his sons offered upon the altar of the burnt offering, and on the altar of incense, and were appointed for all the work of the place most holy, and to make an atonement for Israel, according to all that Moses the servant of God had commanded.

verses.text_plain: And these are the sons of Aaron; Eleazar his son, Phinehas his son, Abishua his son,
verses.verse_html: 50And these are the sons of Aaron; Eleazar his son, Phinehas his son, Abishua his son,

verses.text_plain: Bukki his son, Uzzi his son, Zerahiah his son,
verses.verse_html: 51Bukki his son, Uzzi his son, Zerahiah his son,

verses.text_plain: Meraioth his son, Amariah his son, Ahitub his son,
verses.verse_html: 52Meraioth his son, Amariah his son, Ahitub his son,

verses.text_plain: Zadok his son, Ahimaaz his son.
verses.verse_html: 53Zadok his son, Ahimaaz his son.

verses.text_plain: Now these are their dwelling places throughout their castles in their coasts, of the sons of Aaron, of the families of the Kohathites: for theirs was the lot.
verses.verse_html: 54Now these are their dwelling places throughout their castles in their coasts, of the sons of Aaron, of the families of the Kohathites: for theirs was the lot.

verses.text_plain: And they gave them Hebron in the land of Judah, and the suburbs thereof round about it.
verses.verse_html: 55And they gave them Hebron in the land of Judah, and the suburbs thereof round about it.

verses.text_plain: But the fields of the city, and the villages thereof, they gave to Caleb the son of Jephunneh.
verses.verse_html: 56But the fields of the city, and the villages thereof, they gave to Caleb the son of Jephunneh.

verses.text_plain: And to the sons of Aaron they gave the cities of Judah, namely, Hebron, the city of refuge, and Libnah with her suburbs, and Jattir, and Eshtemoa, with their suburbs,
verses.verse_html: 57And to the sons of Aaron they gave the cities of Judah, namely, Hebron, the city of refuge, and Libnah with her suburbs, and Jattir, and Eshtemoa, with their suburbs,

verses.text_plain: And Hilen with her suburbs, Debir with her suburbs,
verses.verse_html:
58And Hilen with her suburbs, Debir with her suburbs, ▼
▼ Hilen: or, Holon

verses.text_plain: And Ashan with her suburbs, and Beth–shemesh with her suburbs:
verses.verse_html:
59And Ashan with her suburbs, and Beth–shemesh with her suburbs: ▼
▼ Ashan: or, Ain

verses.text_plain: And out of the tribe of Benjamin; Geba with her suburbs, and Alemeth with her suburbs, and Anathoth with her suburbs. All their cities throughout their families were thirteen cities.
verses.verse_html:
60And out of the tribe of Benjamin; Geba with her suburbs, and Alemeth with her suburbs, and Anathoth with her suburbs. All their cities throughout their families were thirteen cities. ▼
▼ Alemeth: or, Almon

verses.text_plain: And unto the sons of Kohath, which were left of the family of that tribe, were cities given out of the half tribe, namely, out of the half tribe of Manasseh, by lot, ten cities.
verses.verse_html: 61And unto the sons of Kohath, which were left of the family of that tribe, were cities given out of the half tribe, namely, out of the half tribe of Manasseh, by lot, ten cities.

verses.text_plain: And to the sons of Gershom throughout their families out of the tribe of Issachar, and out of the tribe of Asher, and out of the tribe of Naphtali, and out of the tribe of Manasseh in Bashan, thirteen cities.
verses.verse_html: 62And to the sons of Gershom throughout their families out of the tribe of Issachar, and out of the tribe of Asher, and out of the tribe of Naphtali, and out of the tribe of Manasseh in Bashan, thirteen cities.

verses.text_plain: Unto the sons of Merari were given by lot, throughout their families, out of the tribe of Reuben, and out of the tribe of Gad, and out of the tribe of Zebulun, twelve cities.
verses.verse_html: 63Unto the sons of Merari were given by lot, throughout their families, out of the tribe of Reuben, and out of the tribe of Gad, and out of the tribe of Zebulun, twelve cities.

verses.text_plain: And the children of Israel gave to the Levites these cities with their suburbs.
verses.verse_html: 64And the children of Israel gave to the Levites these cities with their suburbs.

verses.text_plain: And they gave by lot out of the tribe of the children of Judah, and out of the tribe of the children of Simeon, and out of the tribe of the children of Benjamin, these cities, which are called by their names.
verses.verse_html: 65And they gave by lot out of the tribe of the children of Judah, and out of the tribe of the children of Simeon, and out of the tribe of the children of Benjamin, these cities, which are called by their names.

verses.text_plain: And the residue of the families of the sons of Kohath had cities of their coasts out of the tribe of Ephraim.
verses.verse_html: 66And the residue of the families of the sons of Kohath had cities of their coasts out of the tribe of Ephraim.

verses.text_plain: And they gave unto them, of the cities of refuge, Shechem in mount Ephraim with her suburbs; they gave also Gezer with her suburbs,
verses.verse_html: 67And they gave unto them, of the cities of refuge, Shechem in mount Ephraim with her suburbs; they gave also Gezer with her suburbs,

verses.text_plain: And Jokmeam with her suburbs, and Beth–horon with her suburbs,
verses.verse_html: 68And Jokmeam with her suburbs, and Beth–horon with her suburbs,

verses.text_plain: And Aijalon with her suburbs, and Gath–rimmon with her suburbs:
verses.verse_html: 69And Aijalon with her suburbs, and Gath–rimmon with her suburbs:

verses.text_plain: And out of the half tribe of Manasseh; Aner with her suburbs, and Bileam with her suburbs, for the family of the remnant of the sons of Kohath.
verses.verse_html: 70And out of the half tribe of Manasseh; Aner with her suburbs, and Bileam with her suburbs, for the family of the remnant of the sons of Kohath.

verses.text_plain: Unto the sons of Gershom were given out of the family of the half tribe of Manasseh, Golan in Bashan with her suburbs, and Ashtaroth with her suburbs:
verses.verse_html: 71Unto the sons of Gershom were given out of the family of the half tribe of Manasseh, Golan in Bashan with her suburbs, and Ashtaroth with her suburbs:

verses.text_plain: And out of the tribe of Issachar; Kedesh with her suburbs, Daberath with her suburbs,
verses.verse_html: 72And out of the tribe of Issachar; Kedesh with her suburbs, Daberath with her suburbs,

verses.text_plain: And Ramoth with her suburbs, and Anem with her suburbs:
verses.verse_html: 73And Ramoth with her suburbs, and Anem with her suburbs:

verses.text_plain: And out of the tribe of Asher; Mashal with her suburbs, and Abdon with her suburbs,
verses.verse_html: 74And out of the tribe of Asher; Mashal with her suburbs, and Abdon with her suburbs,

verses.text_plain: And Hukok with her suburbs, and Rehob with her suburbs:
verses.verse_html: 75And Hukok with her suburbs, and Rehob with her suburbs:

verses.text_plain: And out of the tribe of Naphtali; Kedesh in Galilee with her suburbs, and Hammon with her suburbs, and Kirjathaim with her suburbs.
verses.verse_html: 76And out of the tribe of Naphtali; Kedesh in Galilee with her suburbs, and Hammon with her suburbs, and Kirjathaim with her suburbs.

verses.text_plain: Unto the rest of the children of Merari were given out of the tribe of Zebulun, Rimmon with her suburbs, Tabor with her suburbs:
verses.verse_html: 77Unto the rest of the children of Merari were given out of the tribe of Zebulun, Rimmon with her suburbs, Tabor with her suburbs:

verses.text_plain: And on the other side Jordan by Jericho, on the east side of Jordan, were given them out of the tribe of Reuben, Bezer in the wilderness with her suburbs, and Jahzah with her suburbs,
verses.verse_html: 78And on the other side Jordan by Jericho, on the east side of Jordan, were given them out of the tribe of Reuben, Bezer in the wilderness with her suburbs, and Jahzah with her suburbs,

verses.text_plain: Kedemoth also with her suburbs, and Mephaath with her suburbs:
verses.verse_html: 79Kedemoth also with her suburbs, and Mephaath with her suburbs:

verses.text_plain: And out of the tribe of Gad; Ramoth in Gilead with her suburbs, and Mahanaim with her suburbs,
verses.verse_html: 80And out of the tribe of Gad; Ramoth in Gilead with her suburbs, and Mahanaim with her suburbs,

verses.text_plain: And Heshbon with her suburbs, and Jazer with her suburbs.
verses.verse_html: 81And Heshbon with her suburbs, and Jazer with her suburbs.
